To control HDMI output,add/delete "console=fb" on cmdline.txt.
If delete console=fb definition,you can get serial console instead.
 rpi$ more /boot/cmdline.txt
 root=ld0a console=fb


/root/.xinitrc
 setxkbmap -model jp106 jp

